- [x] Use the `SimpleObject` macro and the `InputObject` macro at the same time.

```rust
#[derive(SimpleObject, InputObject)]
#[graphql(input_name = "MyObjectInput")]
struct MyObject {
    #[graphql(default = 10)]
    a: i32,
    b: bool,
